Additional licenses / components
--------------------------------

Some parts are based on other open-source components. Each component that is based 
on another component has a reference to the original component including the original 
license the code was delivered upon. Below is a list of other components / licenses.

Note: if you feel an item is missing in this list, please let us know!

* Catel
  https://github.com/catel/catel
  Original license: MIT

* ControlzEx
  https://github.com/controlzex/controlzex
  Original license: MIT

* Fluent.Ribbon
  https://github.com/fluentribbon/fluent.ribbon
  Original license: MIT
  
* MahApps.Metro
  https://github.com/mahapps/mahapps.metro
  Original license: Ms-PL (compatible with MIT)

* Material Design Icons
  https://materialdesignicons.com/
  Original license: Pictogrammers Free License (compatible with MIT)
  
* Newtonsoft.Json
  https://github.com/JamesNK/Newtonsoft.Json
  Original license: MIT
  
* Orc.Controls
  https://github.com/wildgums/orc.controls
  Original license: MIT
  
* Orc.LogViewer
  https://github.com/wildgums/orc.logviewer
  Original license: MIT
  
* Orc.SystemInfo
  https://github.com/wildgums/orc.systeminfo
  Original license: MIT